data.description: This stunning property in Vancouver is a MUST SEE and offers a charming and peaceful living experience. With 4 bedrooms upstairs PLUS an office on the main level, there's plenty of space for everyone to enjoy. The best part?! You'll have gorgeous territorial views of trees and a pond, providing a serene backdrop for your daily life. Situated in a desirable cul-de-sac, you'll appreciate the quiet and safe environment. The updated kitchen is a true highlight, offering a modern and stylish space to cook and entertain. You'll also find updated flooring throughout, adding a fresh and contemporary touch to the home. This property truly offers the best of both worlds - a tranquil setting with convenient access to nearby amenities.
